**Results found in relation to Q2, on how many studies refer to energy management in air conditioners based on artificial vision:** For Q2: How many studies refer to energy management in air conditioners based on artificial vision? Of the articles found and described by year in Table 1, 15 articles were considered as they are related to energy management, technologies applied in air conditioners, and artificial vision with limited results. Finding a limited study allows the determination that the application of artificial vision techniques in relation to the Internet of Things (IoT) makes it feasible in this research. So, there are also air conditioners with inverter technology, which have a high cost according to the sector where it is used.

