According to the relationship of algorithms shown in Table 11, a comparison was made by analyzing the partial efficiency of each algorithm to obtain a total efficiency (as detailed in **TABLE 12**). Additionally, it is observed that the algorithms of Viola-Jones and Histogram of Oriented Gradients (HOG), whose main characteristic is the detection of faces, which, when mixed with other methods and algorithmic models, manages to detect human actions. This includes detecting the image of a person based on artificial vision considering the authors [W2806990378].

